「留得青山在」係最好嘅結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00728b2804aeb0c472cc98597b34633450399d4c","tid":1233446,"uid":159444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:50:57.000Z","msg":"好重要，大家留意，真心！求大家最少睇第一個post<br />\n<br />\n呢場仗要小心打！我覺得呢位巴打分析得好到位！<br />\n<br />\n[文長，文宣]分析中央打法已經開始由明轉暗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233323</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n為防被抹黑 同商討下一步行動 我建議揾民陣宣佈&quot;暫休&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233591\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233591</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79f9bd43c367a11d2cf1879936b9b3063c54ea41","tid":1233446,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f8ebaf185e5424e826570d4971efc7bd2f399b8","tid":1233446,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:49:51.000Z","msg":"明明講明各有各做 互相扶持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:52:04.000Z","msg":"因為同一招"}]}